# Next.js Project Setup Complete

This workspace contains a Next.js 16.1.3 application with:
- TypeScript
- Tailwind CSS
- ESLint
- App Router

## Important Note
Your current Node.js version (20.1.0) is below the required version (>=20.9.0) for Next.js 16. Please upgrade Node.js to continue development.

## Running the Project
Once Node.js is upgraded, run:
```bash
npm run dev
```

The development server will start at http://localhost:3000
